Brazil ’s decision to cut a tax on
fuel was aimed at preventing a rise of gasoline prices and
didn’t take in consideration imports of  Petroleo Brasileiro SA (PETR4) ,
Antonio Henrique Silveira, head the  Finance Ministry ’s antitrust
arm told reporters today in Brasilia.  To contact the reporter on this story:
